1044
01:23:36,029 --> 01:23:37,190
He was evicted because of an error.

1045
01:23:37,810 --> 01:23:39,851
And he, you know, like was evicted in the winter.

1046
01:23:39,911 --> 01:23:41,912
So it there are all different stories.

1047
01:23:41,952 --> 01:23:43,273
